  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.fasterxml.jackson.core.Versioned, Serializable
    public class DelegatingAnnotationIntrospector
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.introspect.JacksonAnnotationIntrospector
    A DelegatingAnnotationIntrospector is a lightweight extension to JacksonAnnotationIntrospector to trick Jackson into thinking all classes are annotated with @JsonTypeIdResolver(value = SimpleClassNameIdResolver.class) If you add a custom JsonTypeIdResolver annotation it will override the magic annotation from this class.
